<?php $__env->startSection('content'); ?><p>Lily Collins took to Instagram on Sunday to share a series of ethereal snaps in the spot her now-fiance Charlie McDowell popped the question on Friday.</p>

<p>The director asked her to be his wife in the stunning surrounds of Sedona, New Mexico, and Lily, 31, showed off the beauty of the region while dressed in earthy tones.</p>

<p>Posting nighttime snaps, she captioned this: 'New Mexico at Magic Hour.'</p>

